This is very comfortable as well as useful mosque for travelers as well as the local believers.

The masjid is just 600 metres away from the Thanjavur railway station.

There are all the facilities available to refresh and to have a peaceful prayer.

The Haudh' (water tank) of the mosque is a Major attraction, it was full of ornamental fishes but the tank was so clean as well.

Well furnished interior of the masjid is another attraction.

featured_reviews.review_id:
This masjid seems like old ones and is on the main road and very near to the Old Bus Stand just by walkable distance of 10 minutes. Though it's a small mosque, its situated at the central place. I think after this renovation there will be a more place to occupy more people for the prayer.

Either from East Gate bus stop or Thiruvaiyaru Bus stop you can reach it soon. As I know this is the only masjid very near to the Old Bus stand

PS: When I am writing this review this renovation works are going on. Alhamduliah! I think it will be finished soon.
